=========================
DATABASE CONFIGURATION
=========================
Formato:
postgresql+psycopg2://USER@HOST/DB_NAME

DATABASE_URL=postgresql+psycopg2://user@localhost:5432/database_name

=========================
SECURITY
=========================
Clave secreta para JWT (cambiar por una segura)

SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key_here

ALGORITHM=HS256


ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=60

=========================
ENVIRONMENT
=========================
development | production | testing

ENVIRONMENT=development